ty acids)." Abbott Pharmaceutical, Abbott Park, IL.[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[7] Buckley MS, Goff AD, Knapp WE "Fish oil interaction with warfarin." Ann Pharmacother 38 (2004): 50-3', 1767369485);
